            "name": "TheCocktailDB Search Cocktails by Name or First Letter",
            "description": {
              "content": "Search for cocktails by name using the 's' parameter, or browse cocktails starting with a specific letter using the 'f' parameter. Use the 'i' parameter to search for an ingredient by name.",
